        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: align menu items and convert action rows to native NSMenuItems",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- convert Refresh, Settings, About, and Quit from custom `PersistentMenuActionItemView` rows to native `NSMenuItem`s — only Install Update keeps the custom view since it needs an in-place spinner\r\n- add system image names for Settings, About, and Quit so icons render on the native items\r\n- align Cost and Subscription Utilization leading edges to 20pt to match the provider name header (was 14pt)\r\n- reduce Subscription Utilization hover highlight vertical padding 8→6pt\r\n- reduce `PersistentMenuActionItemView` row height 28→22pt to match native item height\r\n- shrink Install Update spinner: `controlSize` small→mini, size 16→12pt\r\n- fix shortcut field font (`smallSystemFontSize` → default menu font) and widen field 38→48pt to prevent clipping\r\n- remove 2pt top/bottom background highlight insets so the selection fills the full row\r\n- remove `persistentRefreshRows` tracking and `updatePersistentRefreshRowsInProgress` (no longer needed)\r\n\r\n## Tests\r\n\r\n- update `StatusMenuPersistentRefreshTests` to reflect native item behavior: Refresh now has an action and no custom view; spinner in-progress tests scoped to `PersistentMenuActionItemView` directly rather than via the Refresh menu item\r\n- full suite: 4427 tests passed\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\n- exact head: `e39cc6f1e1ef1808e7a744ec8ca8804e36da30d9`\r\n- `./Scripts/lint.sh lint`: 0 violations, 0 serious in 1154 files\r\n- `./Scripts/test.sh`: all tests passed\r\n\r\n## Screenshots\r\nBefore:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"306\" height=\"972\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-19 at 1 33 47 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d22b434-76fe-478b-bca8-e2d7c320e461\" />\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"304\" height=\"1025\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-19 at 1 34 16 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/459e1da7-d16f-459a-b9fa-daa16f4726f6\" />\r\n",
